race.description: Greenfields Lodge At Magic Millions Maiden
race.comment: I'M ODETTE (13) ran a solid race on debut at Ascot over 1200m, drawing wide and running on well for a 3-length defeat. She'll be better for that experience and the rise to 1400m looks ideal in what should be a softer maiden. Pike sticks and while she draws wide again, expect her to be charging late. PARTAY (4) ran well on debut at Pinjarra for third, albeit beaten 4.6 lengths. Up to 1400m should suit nicely for him and he could have map advantages over I'M ODETTE. HEAVENLY RAPTURE (11) was okay fresh at Ascot and should be better for it up in trip. EXTREME RULER (2) has had a few chances but was good here last time and has claims. LATORIO (7) next best.
